<plot>Set in Northcross, Connecticut, "Where the Heart Is" followed the dysfunctional lives of the Hathaway family and those near them. The problem of the Hathaway family was quite simple: everyone was having a secret affair with everyone else's wife/husband, resulting in disastrous consequences.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?653962</url></doc>
